            "id": "https://blog.zero251.xyz/posts/docker-compose-configs",
            "content_html": "<ol>\n<li>\n<p>FRPS</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">services:\n  frps_sSDC:\n    image: snowdreamtech/frps:${VERSION}\n    #    container_name: ${CONTAINER_NAME}\n    deploy:\n      resources:\n        limits:\n          cpus: ${CPUS}\n          memory: ${MEMORY_LIMIT}\n    network_mode: host\n    restart: always\n    volumes:\n      - ${APP_PATH}/data/frps.toml:/etc/frp/frps.toml\n      - ${APP_PATH}/data/ssl:/etc/frp/ssl\n    labels:\n      createdBy: &quot;bt_apps&quot;\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>3X-UI</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://blog.zero251.xyz/posts/docker-compose-configs\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.zero251.xyz/posts/docker-compose-configs</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
